description: Try our easy to follow Grilled Salmon With Peach & Avocado recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Grilled Salmon With Peach & Avocado Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Arrange rocket, peaches, avocado, cucumber, onion and chilli onto plates. Top with salmon and season to taste. Drizzle with lime juice, to serve.
